==Serbian==

===Phrase===
'''[[срећан|Срећан]] [[Божић]]'''

# ''Greeting:'' [[Merry Christmas]].

===Usage notes===
This greeting is rarely heard in Serbian language and it literally means ''Happy/Merry Christmas''.  However, the more common greeting is [[Христос се роди#Serbian|Христос се роди]].''

====Roman spelling====
*[[Srećan Božić#Serbian|Srećan Božić]]

====Synonyms====
*[[Христос се роди#Serbian|Христос се роди]]

